Some scripts to create certificates
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


create-set-of-certificates-hierarchical.sh

Create a complete tree of certificates:

 * CA
 * Intermediate Server CA
 * Intermediate Client CA
 * 1 Server Certificate
 * 2 Client Certificates


create-certificates-selfsigned.sh

Creates self-signed certificates. You simply have to list
the name of the certificates (user names) as parameter like:

create-certificates-selfsigned.sh name1 name2 name3
